---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Article',
  headline: 'Best Humbot Alternatives in 2026: Top AI Humanizers',
  description: 'Looking for Humbot alternatives? Compare the top AI text humanization tools including Undetectable Ai, Stealth Writer, Bypassgpt, and more.',
  datePublished: '2026-03-11',
  dateModified: '2026-03-11',
};

const alternatives = [
  {
    name: 'Undetectable Ai',
    slug: 'undetectable-ai',
    description: 'A powerful AI text humanization tool offering advanced humanization with natural results.',
    rating: 4,
    pricing: 'Free plan available',
    pros: [
      'High accuracy',
      'Detailed reports',
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Stealth Writer',
    slug: 'stealth-writer',
    description: 'A powerful AI text humanization tool offering advanced humanization with natural results.',
    rating: 4.5,
    pricing: '$10-30/month',
    pros: [
      'Fast processing',
      'API access',
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Bypassgpt',
    slug: 'bypassgpt',
    description: 'A powerful AI text humanization tool offering advanced humanization with natural results.',
    rating: 4,
    pricing: 'Free + Premium tiers',
    pros: [
      'User-friendly',
      'Bulk processing',
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Smodin',
    slug: 'smodin',
    description: 'A powerful AI text humanization tool offering advanced humanization with natural results.',
    rating: 4.5,
    pricing: 'Starting at $15/mo',
    pros: [
      'Great support',
      'Custom models',
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Quillbot',
    slug: 'quillbot',
    description: 'A powerful AI text humanization tool offering advanced humanization with natural results.',
    rating: 4,
    pricing: 'Free trial available',
    pros: [
      'Affordable',
      'Multiple formats',
    ],
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Best Humbot Alternatives in 2026: Top AI Humanizers"
  description="Looking for Humbot alternatives? Compare the top AI text humanization tools including Undetectable Ai, Stealth Writer, Bypassgpt, and more."
  schema={schema}
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Best Humbot Alternatives in 2026: Top AI Humanizers</h1>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
      Humbot is a popular AI text humanization tool, but it's not the only option. Here are the best alternatives worth considering in 2026.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Look for Humbot Alternatives?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
      While Humbot offers solid AI text humanization capabilities, you might want alternatives for:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-12 space-y-2">
      <li>Better pricing or value for money</li>
      <li>Different feature sets matching your specific needs</li>
      <li>Higher accuracy for your content type</li>
      <li>Better customer support and documentation</li>
      <li>More flexible API integrations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Top Humbot Alternatives</h2>
    <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">
      {alternatives.map((alt, idx) => (
        <div class="border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">{idx + 1}. {alt.name}</h3>
            <div class="text-yellow-500 font-bold">{alt.rating} ★</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">{alt.description}</p>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <strong>Pricing:</strong> {alt.pricing}
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <strong>Key Advantages:</strong>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2">
              {alt.pros.map(pro => <li>{pro}</li>)}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a 
            href={`/compare/humbot-vs-${alt.slug}`}
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold"
          >
            Compare Humbot vs {alt.name} →
          </a>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">How to Choose the Right Alternative</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      When evaluating Humbot alternatives, consider these factors:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-12 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Test with your specific content type</li>
      <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> Compare value across free trials and paid tiers</li>
      <li><strong>Features:</strong> Match capabilities to your workflow needs</li>
      <li><strong>Integration:</strong> Check API availability and compatibility</li>
      <li><strong>Support:</strong> Evaluate documentation and customer service</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Conclusion</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
      Humbot is a solid choice, but these alternatives offer compelling features and value. Test free trials to find the best AI text humanization tool for your specific needs.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
